Examples Example: Using getDay The second statement below assigns the value 1 to weekday, based on the value of the Date object Xmas95. December 25, 1995, is a Monday.
Xmas95 = new Date("December 25, 1995 23:15:00"); weekday = Xmas95.getDay();

